The Bad Guys: Breaking In is an American animated television series based on the 2022 film The Bad Guys, which in turn is based on the graphic novel series of the same name. Like the two television specials that came before, the series serves as a prequel to the original film. Godere, Ajeigbe, Ceballos, Diamantopoulos and Low all reprise their roles from the shorts; none of the films' original cast return.
The series was released via Netflix on November 6, 2025.
